
= find carsharing service providers in your area with this international list. 

URL = http://carsharing.net/where.html


=Examples=
    
* Zimride [http://www.zimride.com/], eRideShare & [[Carpooling]].com (Europe) - Find a ride or offer a ride on these top [[Ridesharing Platforms]]. And check out Avego [http://avego.com/] for [[Real Time Ridesharing]] through a mobile app.
    
* [[ZipCar]] - the largest fleet-based carsharing service in the world.
    
* [[RelayRides]], Getaround, [[Just Share It]], and Whipcar (UK) - Rent cars to or from neighbors using the leaders of the peer to peer carsharing movement.
    
* [[Weeels]] - order cabs and share rides with this smartphone app.


